0 transition-colors\">\n              View on Amazon →\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      \n      <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n        <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81RJDOvNozL._AC_UY218_.jpg\" alt=\"Alcedo Sterile Sutures Kit 28-Piece - Sterile Surgical Equipment\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-48 object-contain bg-slate-50 mb-4\">\n        <h3 data-asin=\"B0BX4S7RSP\" class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2\">Alcedo Sterile Sutures Kit — 28 Pieces</h3>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n          <span class=\"bg-lime text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold\">4.7★</span>\n          <span class=\"bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs\">$$</span>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm mb-3\">\n          Nearly identical to the kit above — same configuration, same quality tier. Pick whichever's in stock or cheaper when you order.\n        </p>\n        <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BX4S7RSP?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-flame text-white text-sm font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors\">\n          Check Price →\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <div class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl my-10 text-center\">\n    <span class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-flame\">49</span>\n    <p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mt-2\">pieces in the most comprehensive kit — enough for multiple emergencies over years of use</p>\n  </div>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"mb-12\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6\">For Maximum Preparedness: The Big Kits</h2>\n    \n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n      <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5\">\n          <div class=\"w-full sm:w-44 shrink-0\">\n            <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/91sEjm1d0yL._AC_UY218_.jpg\" alt=\"Sterile Mixed Sutures 49-Piece Kit - Sterile Surgical Equipment\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-44 object-contain bg-slate-50\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n            <h3 data-asin=\"B075D9J56D\" class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2\">Sterile Mixed Sutures — 49-Piece Military-Style Kit</h3>\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n              <span class=\"bg-lime text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold\">4.7★</span>\n              <span class=\"bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs\">$$</span>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm mb-3\">\n              Marketed for military/survival use, which means it's designed for rough conditions and long storage. Excellent variety of suture sizes. If you're sending to someone in a rural area far from hospitals, this is the one.\n            </p>\n            <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B075D9J56D?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-flame text-white text-sm font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors\">\n              View on Amazon →\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5\">\n          <div class=\"w-full sm:w-44 shrink-0\">\n            <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/i