>Sutures alone aren't enough. These basics round out a proper wound care setup.</p>\n    \n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5\">\n      \n      <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n        <span class=\"bg-royal text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase mb-3 inline-block\">Budget Essential</span>\n        <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/91fSuv1Ne9L._AC_UY218_.jpg\" alt=\"All Health Wound Care Kit 40-Piece - Sterile Surgical Equipment\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-40 object-contain bg-slate-50 mb-3\">\n        <h3 data-asin=\"B07FYDFGVD\" class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2\">All Health Wound Care Kit — 40 Pieces</h3>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\">\n          <span class=\"bg-lime text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold\">4.7★</span>\n          <span class=\"bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs\">$</span>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm mb-3\">The basics: gauze, tape, antiseptic wipes. No sutures, but perfect alongside a suture kit. Throw one in every package.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07FYDFGVD?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-3 py-2 rounded-full bg-flame text-white text-xs font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors\">\n          View on Amazon →\n        </a>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n        <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71A7pSJlSxL._AC_UY218_.jpg\" alt=\"Sterile Cotton Tipped Applicators Box of 100 - Sterile Surgical Equipment\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-40 object-contain bg-slate-50 mb-3\">\n        <h3 data-asin=\"B082BGC3CB\" class=